The precious '''Alzoc pearls''' were found on [[Alzoc III/Legends|Alzoc III]].

The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] used the [[Talz/Legends|Talz]] to heavily [[Mining/Legends|mine]] the planet for raw materials, and by coincidence these valuable pearls were found, also.

They could be used for decorations especially for knife handles.

